Title: Pomax.github.io
Description: Did you know that there isn't just a dumb, simple Windows utility for turning a joystick or game controller into a MIDI device? I have VKB-Sim rudder pedals because I might like flight sim a little too much and not a minute goes by while I'm sitting at my desk that my feet don't think they're resting on sostenuto and sustain pedals. Because there's also a keyboard sitting on my desk.
